    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my pride and joy. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always kept it tucked away in the garage and hand-washed it every weekend. It still has that incredible showroom feel that\u2019ll put a huge smile on your face the moment you settle into the driver's seat. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth as silk and ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape, practically looking like it just rolled off the lot! Come on over and take a look; I\u2019d love to talk shop and show you exactly why this one is so special.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
